594
00:42:44,344 --> 00:42:45,784
Hah?

595
00:42:47,588 --> 00:42:49,188
Wawwa?

596
00:42:49,188 --> 00:42:50,758
Tulip.

597
00:42:50,758 --> 00:42:55,558
