613
00:43:55,832 --> 00:43:59,268
Tidak apa-apa. Tenanglah.

614
00:43:59,268 --> 00:44:01,384
Menakutkan sekali.

615
00:44:09,188 --> 00:44:11,078
Kamu sudah pulang.

616
00:44:11,078 --> 00:44:13,268
